874
00:36:59,575 --> 00:37:01,120
how it feels to have lost the loved one

875
00:37:02,600 --> 00:37:03,879
and been left alone.

876
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:14,879
Hadn’t it been for me,

877
00:37:17,399 --> 00:37:19,199
you wouldn’t have suffered so much.

878
