920
00:39:56,439 --> 00:39:57,525
It was my duty

921
00:39:57,639 --> 00:39:58,879
to end the disaster.

922
00:39:59,520 --> 00:40:00,800
Dazheng keeps

923
00:40:01,159 --> 00:40:03,560
